snippet.title: Amber Valletta’s Model Activism
snippet.description:
With 16 Vogue covers under her belt, the original supermodel of the 1990s is increasingly devoting her energy to activism, fighting climate change and promoting a sustainable future for fashion. Here, the 46-year-old L.A. resident salutes her hero, Jane Fonda, and cites California’s homegrown brands as the pioneers in finding a solution to fashion’s biggest problems.
